OL,3,CMet Office issues ice warning as
OL,4,Ctemperatures set to drop
OL,6,FWelsh motorists and pedestrians are
OL,7,Fbeing urged to take extra care tonight
OL,8,Fas a Met Office weather warning for
OL,9,Fice comes into force across the
OL,10,Fmajority of the country.
OL,12,FThe yellow alert is set to take effect
OL,13,Ffrom 10pm tonight (Sunday) and will
OL,14,Fremain in place until 9am on Monday
OL,15,Fmorning. The warning covers almost all
OL,16,Fof Wales, with only Wrexham and
OL,17,FFlintshire currently excluded from the
OL,18,Falert area.
